<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\malloc\_alloca">_alloca</sample>
    <title> _alloca</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> mal_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>在栈中分配的内存数。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>void *</return_val>
        <func_name>_alloca</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>size_t</param_type>
                <param_name>size</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>在栈中分配内存。</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>_alloca返回所分配空间的无类型指针，以保证适用于任一对象类型。为了得到所需类型的指针，应对返回值进行类型转换。如果空间分配失败，产生栈溢出例外。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>_alloca函数从栈中分配所需的字节数。当所调用的函数退出时，所分配的空间自动被回收。因此，不必通过由alloca函数返回的指针值作为参数去释放所分配的空间。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>_alloca</routine_name>
            <headerfile>malloc.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2004,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* _alloca.cpp: This program uses _alloca function to
 * allocates memory on the stack.
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;
#include &lt;malloc.h&gt;

#define NUM 0x80

int main()
{
    int *intArray;

    intArray = (int*)_alloca(sizeof(int) * NUM);
    printf(&quot;Integer allocating (number: %d)  OK!\n&quot;, sizeof(int) * NUM);

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
Integer allocating (number: 512)  OK!
</result>

    

